title: World Epoch
brief: Dominic Williams, founder of the Dfinity Foundation, has announced his intention to create a project to combat media propaganda.
blurb:
Dominic Williams, founder of the Dfinity Foundation, has announced his intention to create a project to combat media propaganda. This idea inspired our team to create an NFT collection dedicated to famous historical eras of mankind.

History contributes to the evaluation of the past, so that humanity can understand and make sense of all the events that occurred.

Our collection is a collection of those events ĸ which we know, and perhaps you have already guessed, will be hosted on the blockchain of the Internet computer. We are convinced that decentralized blockchain technology is a defense against censorship.

It is important to keep the lessons of history intact, and this is our way of paying tribute to all those who have contributed to human culture.

We must always remember: Those who forget the lessons of history are doomed to repeat them!
